Machinae Supremacy - Live at Assembly (2011)

This is high-quality loseless audio of Machinae Supremacy's show, recorded at Assembly Summer demoparty @ Hartwall Areena, Helsinki on Aug 4th 2011. This recording was fully remastered, with some parts being partially re-recorded, for better listener's experience.
